        SimpliFly makes becoming a pilot simple. SimpliFly's flexible pilot training programs are designed to accommodate your lifestyle while allowing you to pursue your dream of becoming a pilot. With our flexible programs, you have the freedom to tailor your training to your availability, that way you can balance your personal commitments with your passion for flying.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col px-5 gap-3 pb-5">
        <div class="flex flex-row ">
          <div class="text-sky-500 pr-2 font-extrabold">✈</div>
          <h3 class="lg:px-10 pl-4 p-text text-left">Personalized schedule</h3>
